flowRoot.flowPara: Short Explain over the chart on the Top on this text bar. Here you can see all SSD's per Physical Server. The Physical Server can choosen on the navBar on the right side. On the chart the administrator can see all SSD's from a physical Servers and their write endurance. If a SSD's get in touch with the Line a Notification will send to the Administrator and the SSD will declared on the Right navBar. Also you can see on the Chart, which SSD will work more then other SSD's.
A Threshold, which shows the SSD which has reached the max. of write endurance
